## 3. Docker (полный конспект)

### 3.1. Базовые команды

```bash
docker run -d -p 8080:80 --name my-nginx nginx:latest
```

| Часть | Что значит |
|-------|------------|
| `docker run` | Запустить контейнер. |
| `-d` | Запустить в фоне. |
| `-p 8080:80` | Проброс портов. |
| `--name my-nginx` | Дать имя контейнеру. |
| `nginx:latest` | Образ Nginx (последняя версия). |

**Если порт занят:**
```bash
docker network prune -f
```

---

### 3.2. Docker Compose

**Полный файл `docker-compose.yml`**
```yaml
services:
  web:
    image: nginx:latest
    container_name: my-nginx
    networks:
      - monitoring-net
    ports:
      - "8081:80"
    restart: unless-stopped

  grafana:
    image: grafana/grafana:latest
    container_name: my-grafana
    networks:
      - monitoring-net
    ports:
      - "3000:3000"
    restart: unless-stopped

  mysql:
    image: mysql:latest
    container_name: my-mysql
    networks:
      - monitoring-net
    environment:
      MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD: rootpass123
      MYSQL_DATABASE: testdb
      MYSQL_USER: testuser
      MYSQL_PASSWORD: testpass123
    ports:
      - "3306:3306"
    restart: unless-stopped

  portainer:
    image: portainer/portainer-ce:latest
    container_name: my-portainer
    networks:
      - monitoring-net
    ports:
      - "8000:8000"
      - "9443:9443"
    volumes:
      - /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock
      - portainer-data:/data
    restart: unless-stopped

  prometheus:
    image: prom/prometheus:latest
    container_name: my-prometheus
    networks:
      - monitoring-net
    ports:
      - "9090:9090"
    restart: unless-stopped

  node-exporter:
    image: prom/node-exporter:latest
    container_name: my-node-exporter
    networks:
      - monitoring-net
    ports:
      - "9100:9100"
    restart: unless-stopped

  cadvisor:
    image: gcr.io/cadvisor/cadvisor:latest
    container_name: my-cadvisor
    networks:
      - monitoring-net
    ports:
      - "8080:8080"
    volumes:
      - /:/rootfs:ro
      - /var/run:/var/run:ro
      - /sys:/sys:ro
      - /var/lib/docker/:/var/lib/docker:ro
      - /dev/disk/:/dev/disk:ro
    privileged: true
    restart: unless-stopped

  nginx-proxy:
    image: nginx:latest
    container_name: my-nginx-proxy
    networks:
      - monitoring-net
    ports:
      - "80:80"
    volumes:
      - ./nginx.conf:/etc/nginx/nginx.conf:ro
    depends_on:
      - grafana
    restart: unless-stopped

volumes:
  portainer-data:
  grafana-data:

networks:
  monitoring-net:
    driver: bridge
```

**Команды для Compose:**
```bash
docker compose up -d     # запустить всё
docker compose down       # остановить всё
docker ps                 # список контейнеров
```

